OL,3,C'An astonishing mistake': Former
OL,4,CJersey Zoo employee slams exhibit
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FJersey Zoo's former Head of Mammals
OL,8,Fhas questioned the decision to
OL,9,Fpermanently close the park's
OL,10,FLivingstone bat enclosure, calling it
OL,11,F"an astonishing mistake."
OL,13,FDominic Wormell worked for Durrell's
OL,14,FWildlife Conservation Trust, who built
OL,15,Fthe zoo, for 34 years.
OL,17,FHe believes the recent decision to
OL,18,Frehome the bats is both financially
OL,19,Funnecessary and highly damaging to the
OL,20,Fsurvival of the endangered fruit bat
OL,21,Fspecies.
