OL,3,C'An astonishing mistake': Former
OL,4,CJersey Zoo employee slams exhibit
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FBen Matthews, Curator of Mammals at
OL,8,FJersey Zoo, has said it would cost at
OL,9,Fleast #1,000,000 to repair their
OL,10,Fpermanent tunnel exhibition after
OL,11,Fstorm damage earlier this year.
OL,13,FHowever, Wormell has queried this
OL,14,Ffigure, instead suggesting that
OL,15,Frepairing the exhibition would cost as
OL,16,Flittle as #50,000 - #60,000.
OL,18,F"If they rebuilt it with the same
OL,19,Fmodel we used, it wouldn't cost that
OL,20,Fmuch," Worrell argued.
