OL,7,FHe added: "Polly-tunnels are cheap,
OL,8,Fthe materials involved have guarantees
OL,9,Fof many years, and last time we
OL,10,Frebuilt the roof it was essentially
OL,11,Fdone by volunteers.
OL,13,F"It's scaffolding and cladding - it's
OL,14,Flow cost."
OL,16,FJersey Zoo currently houses 75% of the
OL,17,Fglobal captive population of
OL,18,FLivingstone fruit bats, and has been
OL,19,Flooking after the endangered species
OL,20,Fsince 1992.
