OL,7,FThe bats have been kept in temporary
OL,8,Faccommodation since April, after an
OL,9,Finfection outbreak killed 10 of the
OL,10,Froost.
OL,12,FWormell added that he "cannot fathom
OL,13,Fthe decision."
OL,15,F"These bats come from small islands in
OL,16,Fthe Indian Ocean, which were decimated
OL,17,Fby a typhoon killing 30% of the
OL,18,Fpopulation five years ago, leaving
OL,19,Fjust 1200 - 1400 of these bats alive
OL,20,Fin the wild.
