OL,3,C'An astonishing mistake': Former
OL,4,CJersey Zoo employee slams exhibit
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FMatt Goetz, interim Zoological
OL,8,FDirector at the Trust, said: "We're
OL,9,Fnow at a point where any decision or
OL,10,Finvestment made regarding their
OL,11,Fpermanent enclosure would not align
OL,12,Fwith how long we can keep them in
OL,13,Ftheir temporary home without
OL,14,Fencountering problems."
OL,16,FHe also denied that the exhibit could
OL,17,Fbe repaired for the price Wormell
OL,18,Fsuggested, without significantly
OL,19,Flowering their structural and welfare
OL,20,Fstandards.
