OL,3,C'An astonishing mistake': Former
OL,4,CJersey Zoo employee slams exhibit
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FGoetz said: "There has been long-term
OL,8,Fdeterioration of the bat tunnel, which
OL,9,Fwe have invested tens of thousands of
OL,10,Fpounds in repairs to upkeep.
OL,12,F"We now have to adhere to new planning
OL,13,Fregulations, and rising costs in
OL,14,Falmost everything ranging from
OL,15,Fmaterials to staff.
OL,17,F"We would like to keep the door open
OL,18,Ffor the bats to return one day."
